# 🌟 FutureMe – Future Letter Generator

## 📖 Project Overview

**FutureMe – Future Letter Generator** is a beginner-friendly Python application that allows users to write a digital letter to their future self, set personal goals, and generate a beautifully formatted HTML report. The project combines **Python Fundamentals**, **HTML**, and **CSS** to create a simple digital time capsule that inspires users to reflect on their dreams and future aspirations.

This project was developed as part of the **AI Powered Python Internship** and is ideal for beginners learning Python and basic web technologies.

