# ▶️ How to Run

1. Open **Google Colab**.
2. Create a new notebook.
3. Copy and paste the project code.
4. Run the notebook from top to bottom.
5. Enter your personal information.
6. Add your future goals.
7. Write your letter.
8. View your personalized HTML report.

